"title": "6696: necessity",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6696",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>That which makes certain actions or events occur. Scripture relates it to particular events which must happen to bring about God's plan of salvation and also to the behaviour that believers are to adopt as a result of their commitment to Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The necessity of Jesus Christ's death and resurrection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25-Luke24:27\">LUK 24:25–24:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:25\">LUK 17:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44-Luke24:47\">LUK 24:44–24:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:14-John3:15\">JHN 3:14–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:9\">JHN 20:9</a></p>\n<h2>The necessity of Jesus Christ's obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:42-Luke4:44\">LUK 4:42–4:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:14-Matt3:15\">MAT 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:49\">LUK 2:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:31-Luke13:33\">LUK 13:31–13:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:4\">JHN 4:4</a> <em>The necessity lay in Jesus Christ's mission not in geography</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:4\">JHN 9:4</a></p>\n<h2>The necessity of the events leading to the end times</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:1\">REV 1:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:7-Mark13:8\">MRK 13:7–13:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:6-Matt24:8\">MAT 24:6–24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:9-Luke21:11\">LUK 21:9–21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:10\">MRK 13:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:14\">MAT 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:50-1Cor15:55\">1CO 15:50–15:55</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:1\">REV 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:1-Rev20:3\">REV 20:1–20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:6\">REV 22:6</a></p>\n<h2>Necessity and the law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:3\">GAL 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:7\">JHN 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:3\">HEB 5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:16\">HEB 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:22-Heb9:23\">HEB 9:22–9:23</a></p>\n<h2>Necessity in the life of the Christian</h2>\n<h3>The necessity of conversion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:5-John3:7\">JHN 3:5–3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:2-Matt18:3\">MAT 18:2–18:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:3\">JHN 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:30\">ACT 17:30</a></p>\n<h3>The necessity of godly behaviour</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1-Rom15:2\">ROM 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:14-1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:14–3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:7-1Tim4:8\">1TI 4:7–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22-2Tim2:24\">2TI 2:22–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:11-Titus2:14\">TIT 2:11–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Necessity in the life of Paul</h2>\n<h3>The necessity of Paul's calling</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:15-Acts9:16\">ACT 9:15–9:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:6\">ACT 9:6</a></p>\n<h3>The necessity of Paul's preaching of the gospel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:46\">ACT 13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:21\">ACT 19:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">ACT 23:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:21-Acts27:25\">ACT 27:21–27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:19\">ACT 28:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:14\">ROM 1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:16-1Cor9:18\">1CO 9:16–9:18</a></p>\n<h2>The paradoxes of necessity</h2>\n<h3>Freedom and necessity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:18\">ROM 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:19-1Cor9:23\">1CO 9:19–9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:7\">2CO 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:14\">PHM 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Responsibility and necessity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:7\">MAT 18:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:1\">LUK 17:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:22\">LUK 22:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">MAT 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:21\">MRK 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a></p>",
